name: Chrome & Cane Dining Chair with Arms - Dark Oak
description: The Chrome & Cane Rattan Dining Chair with Arms – Dark Oak features an industrial chrome and solid oak framework, smooth dark oak arms, with a handwoven cane rattan seat and backrest. Designed to bring both visual and physical lightness, the cantilevered design gives the illusion of a floating seat, complemented by contrasting materials of soft cane, warm dark oak, and the fluid chrome frame.
